  "detailed_description": "Experience upgraded version of bomberman!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069000/extras/e23bb568a8060579e1413fbc20889981.avif?t=1725103358\" width=603 height=93 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>The evil Lord of Skull kidnapped all your fellows from the village and you have to rescue them my friend. <br>Use bombs to fight the freedom for one you love. You are the hope, you are the Rescue Bomber!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069000/extras/677a9d19ff2d84fb2a0651505957e23d.avif?t=1725103358\" width=598 height=198 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 game modes with bosses included<br></li><li>60 levels to beat in story mode<br></li><li>Story mode local cooperation with another player<br></li><li>Simple character upgrade system<br></li><li>Local VS mode up to 4 people with computer or other players<br></li><li>Challenging difficulty, specifically on higher levels<br></li><li>Character painting system<br></li><li>29 in game achievements</li></ul>",
